NPCDialogue.LocalizedString: WHOAH! THIS PATH... IT DOESN'T NORMALLY HAVE A GIANT METAL DISC STUCK IN IT... @WHAT HAPPENED, BUNNY DUDE?
HUGE SAWBLADE, MATE. CAME FLYING DOWN. NEARLY CLEAVED ME IN 'TWAIN. @MY LIFE... IT FLASHED BEFORE MY VERY EYES...
OH MAN... SCARY STUFF... ARE YOU OK?
I'M ALRIGHT, MATE. @IT WAS QUITE A USEFUL FLASHBACK, ACTUALLY... @...I COULD SEE WHERE I'D LOST MY KEYS.
JOT, WE CAN'T CARRY ON UP THIS PATH... LET'S FIND ANOTHER WAY AROUND!
